=======

Volume One includes 12 animated short films available for the first time
on Blu-ray. All 12 shorts were produced by Max Fleischer and directed by
his brother Dave Fleischer. Featuring the voices of Mae Questel, Bonnie
Poe and Ann Little as Betty Boop. Also featuring guest voices of Cab
Calloway, Jack Mercer, William Pennell and The Royal Samoans.

Volume One includes the following shorts:

*Chess Nuts (1932)*

*Betty Boop, M.D. (1932)*

*Betty Boop's Bamboo Isle (1932)*

*Betty Boop for President (1932)*

*Betty Boop's Penthouse (1933)*

*Betty Boop's Birthday Party (1933)*

*Betty Boop's May Party (1933)*

*Betty Boop's Halloween Party (1933)*

*Betty Boop's Rise to Fame (1934)*

*Betty Boop's Trial (1934)*

*Betty Boop's Life Guard (1934*

*The Foxy Hunter (1937)*
